OL,3,CBirmingham coalition talks 'positive
OL,4,Cand productive', says Lib Dem leader
OL,6,FCoalition talks between councillors
OL,7,Fseeking to run Birmingham City Council
OL,8,Fhave been described as "positive and
OL,9,Fproductive" by the Liberal Democrat
OL,10,Fgroup leader.
OL,12,FThe comments follow the adjournment of
OL,13,Fthe authority's first full council
OL,14,Fmeeting since the local elections.
OL,26,@pD@XOUqD@KO]
