OL,3,CBirmingham coalition talks 'positive
OL,4,Cand productive', says Lib Dem leader
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News Central,
OL,7,FCouncillor Roger Harmer said
OL,8,Fdiscussions between the Liberal
OL,9,FDemocrats, Greens and some independent
OL,10,Fcouncillors were continuing "at pace",
OL,11,Falthough no decision has yet been made
OL,12,Fover who would become the council's
OL,13,Fnext leader.
OL,15,FIt comes after Tuesday's full council
OL,16,Fmeeting, the first involving all 101
OL,17,Fnewly elected councillors, was
OL,18,Fadjourned without a new administration
OL,19,Fbeing confirmed.
OL,26,@rD@]OUrD@eO]
