OL,3,CBirmingham coalition talks 'positive
OL,4,Cand productive', says Lib Dem leader
OL,6,FIn a joint statement released after
OL,7,Fthe meeting, the Green, Liberal
OL,8,FDemocrat and Better Birmingham
OL,9,FIndependent groups said they were
OL,10,Fworking together to establish a
OL,11,F"sustainable administration" for the
OL,12,Fcity.
OL,14,FThe statement said: "Following
OL,15,Ftonight's council meeting, we
OL,16,Funderstand there are still many
OL,17,Fquestions about the Council's
OL,18,Fleadership.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@\O]vD@UOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/9
