OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1779271612
OL,3,CBirmingham coalition talks 'positive
OL,4,Cand productive', says Lib Dem leader
OL,6,F"As Leaders of the Green, Liberal
OL,7,FDemocrat, and Better Birmingham
OL,8,FGroups, we are tonight making clear
OL,9,Four commitment to come together for a
OL,10,Fsafer, greener and fairer city.
OL,12,F"We are working to create a
OL,13,Fsustainable administration to serve
OL,14,FBirmingham's residents. We call on
OL,15,Fother councillors who share our aim of
OL,16,Fa fairer city to support us."
OL,18,F"We are working hard to finalise an
OL,19,Fagreement soon, so we can give the
OL,20,Fleadership the Council and the city
OL,21,Fdeserves."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUzD@AOU}D@JO]
