OL,3,CBirmingham coalition talks 'positive
OL,4,Cand productive', says Lib Dem leader
OL,6,FThe statement was signed by Green
OL,7,Fgroup leader Councillor Julien
OL,8,FPritchard, Liberal Democrat leader
OL,9,FCouncillor Roger Harmer and Better
OL,10,FBirmingham group leader Councillor
OL,11,FHarris Kaliq.
OL,13,FSpeaking after the meeting, Councillor
OL,14,FHarmer also suggested council officers
OL,15,Fshould "look over" the proposed bin
OL,16,Fstrike deal agreed with Labour before
OL,17,Fthe election.
OL,26,@wD@HOUwD@RO]
