OL,3,CBirmingham coalition talks 'positive
OL,4,Cand productive', says Lib Dem leader
OL,6,FUnite the Union has been urging
OL,7,Fcouncillors to quickly form an
OL,8,Fadministration so negotiations can be
OL,9,Fcompleted and striking bin workers can
OL,10,Freturn to work.
OL,12,FBirmingham City Council remains
OL,13,Fwithout a clear ruling administration
OL,14,Falmost two weeks after the local
OL,15,Felections.
OL,17,FReform UK, despite emerging as the
OL,18,Flargest group with 23 councillors,
OL,19,Fruled itself out of coalition
OL,20,Fdiscussions, saying it had "no viable
OL,21,Froute" to forming an administration.
OL,26,@|D@\OU}D@FO]
