OL,3,CBirmingham coalition talks 'positive
OL,4,Cand productive', says Lib Dem leader
OL,6,FLabour, which holds 17 seats, also
OL,7,Fconfirmed on Friday it would not enter
OL,8,Fany coalition or power-sharing
OL,9,Farrangement with other parties.
OL,11,FThe Greens hold 19 councillors and the
OL,12,FLiberal Democrats 12, leaving them
OL,13,Fshort of the 51 seats required for a
OL,14,Fmajority, meaning support from
OL,15,Findependents or smaller groups may be
OL,16,Fessential.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/9
