OL,3,CBirmingham coalition talks 'positive
OL,4,Cand productive', says Lib Dem leader
OL,6,FThe Conservatives, who hold 16 seats,
OL,7,Falso appeared to distance themselves
OL,8,Ffrom coalition talks, with one senior
OL,9,Ffigure warning that "any coalition
OL,10,Fthat tries to govern from the extremes
OL,11,Fwill fail."
OL,13,FThe political negotiations come amid
OL,14,Fheightened sensitivity around
OL,15,Fcoalition-building following events in
OL,16,FWorcestershire, where a proposed
OL,17,FConservative-Green coalition collapsed
OL,18,Fwithin hours and led to disciplinary
OL,19,Faction within the Conservative Party.
OL,26,@qD@UOUsD@KO]
